<p>According to the latest report by IMARC Group, titled “<strong>Ceramic Sanitary Ware Market</strong><strong>: Global Industry Trends, Share, Size, Growth, Opportunity and Forecast 2020-2025,</strong>” the global ceramic sanitary ware market size reached US$ 44.2 Billion in 2019. Ceramic sanitary ware includes bathroom accessories made from clay and permanently hardened by heat. They have a glossy surface for easy cleaning, excellent resistance to chemicals and can withstand more than 400 kg load. Ceramic sanitary wares have evolved and are nowadays available in various designs, textures, colors, shapes and sizes in the global market.</p>

